    "body": "2021/03/29 - Mark your Calendar: We are pleased to inform the community that the DSLA utility token will be listed on the KuCoin cryptocurrency exchange on Tuesday, March 30th, 2021 at 11am UTC ! 🎉 KuCoin is a Top 10 CoinMarketCap exchange, with more than $1B in daily trading volume. This major exchange listing will further the cryptocurrency community to acquire DSLA utility tokens in preparation for the DSLA Protocol mainnet launch. 👉 DSLA will debut trading under the DSLA/USDT and DSLA/BTC pair. 🗣 Official KuCoin accouncement: https://www. kucoin. com/news/en-dsla-gets-listed-on-kucoin Registration &amp; Deposit: Get ready for takeoff 🚀: ☝️ We strongly advise you sign up to KuCoin now for a smooth trading experience on d-day. About DSLA Protocol: DSLA Protocol is a risk management framework that enables developers and infrastructure operators to reduce their users exposure to service delays, interruptions and financial losses, using self-executing service level agreements, bonus-malus insurance policies, and crowdfunded liquidity pools. Its flagship use case is to offset the financial losses of proof-of-stake delegators and DeFi users, while incentivizing the good performance and reliability of staking pool operators and DeFi service providers such as Uniswap (AMM) and OpenSea (NFT). To learn more about DSLA Protocol, please visit stacktical. com, browse our official blog, and follow @stacktical on Twitter. "
